#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/algs_include.rst:8
msgid ""
"The *algorithm id* is displayed when you hover over the algorithm in the "
"Processing Toolbox. The *parameter dictionary* provides the parameter NAMEs "
"and values. See :ref:`processing_console` for details on how to run "
"processing algorithms from the Python console."
msgstr ""
"*ID algoritma* se prikazuje kada pređete mišem preko algoritma u kutiji sa "
"alatkama Obrade. *Rečnik parametara* daje NAZIVe i vrednosti parametara. "
"Pogledajte :ref:`processing_console` za detalje o pokretanju algoritama "
"obrade iz Python konzole."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:195
msgid "Cell stack percentile"
msgstr "Percentil steka ćelija"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:197
msgid ""
"Calculates the cell-wise percentile value of a stack of rasters and writes "
"the results to an output raster. The percentile to return is determined by "
"the percentile input value (ranges between 0 and 1). At each cell location, "
"the specified percentile is obtained using the respective value from the "
"stack of all overlaid and sorted cell values of the input rasters."
msgstr ""
"Računa vrednost percentila po ćeliji za stek rastera i upisuje rezultate u "
"izlazni raster. Percentil koji se vraća određuje se ulaznom vrednošću "
"percentila (opseg između 0 i 1). Na svakoj lokaciji ćelije, zadati percentil"
" se dobija pomoću odgovarajuće vrednosti iz steka svih preklopljenih i "
"sortiranih vrednosti ćelija ulaznih rastera."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:203
msgid "There are three methods for percentile calculation:"
msgstr "Postoje tri metoda za računanje percentila:"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:205
msgid ""
"Nearest rank: returns the value that is nearest to the specified percentile"
msgstr "Najbliži rang: vraća vrednost koja je najbliža zadatom percentilu"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:209
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:391
msgid ""
"The linear interpolation methods return the unique values for different "
"percentiles. Both interpolation methods follow their counterpart methods "
"implemented by `LibreOffice <https://help.libreoffice.org/latest/en-"
"US/text/scalc/01/04060184.html?DbPAR=CALC#bm_id3148807>`_ or Microsoft "
"Excel."
msgstr ""
"Metodi linearne interpolacije vraćaju jedinstvene vrednosti za različite "
"percentile. Oba metoda interpolacije prate svoje odgovarajuće metode koje "
"implementiraju `LibreOffice <https://help.libreoffice.org/latest/en-"
"US/text/scalc/01/04060184.html?DbPAR=CALC#bm_id3148807>`_ ili Microsoft "
"Excel."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:224
msgid "Percentile = 0.25. ``NoData`` cells (grey) are ignored."
msgstr "Percentil = 0.25. ``NoData`` ćelije (sive) se zanemaruju."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:257
msgid ""
"0 --- Nearest rank: returns the value that is nearest to the specified "
"percentile"
msgstr ""
"0 --- Najbliži rang: vraća vrednost koja je najbliža zadatom percentilu"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:258
msgid "1 --- Inclusive linear interpolation (PERCENTILE.INC)"
msgstr "1 --- Uključiva linearna interpolacija (PERCENTILE.INC)"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:259
msgid "2 --- Exclusive linear interpolation (PERCENTILE.EXC)"
msgstr "2 --- Isključiva linearna interpolacija (PERCENTILE.EXC)"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:260
msgid "**Percentile**"
msgstr "**Percentil**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:264
msgid "Default: 0.25"
msgstr "Podrazumevano: 0.25"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:265
msgid ""
"Value to rank among the respective values in the stack of all overlaid and "
"sorted cell values from the input rasters. Between 0 and 1."
msgstr ""
"Vrednost koja se rangira među odgovarajućim vrednostima u steku svih "
"preklopljenih i sortiranih vrednosti ćelija iz ulaznih rastera. Između 0 i "
"1."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:366
msgid "**Algorithm ID**: ``native:cellstackpercentile``"
msgstr "**ID algoritma**: ``native:cellstackpercentile``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:376
msgid "Cell stack percentrank from raster layer"
msgstr "Procentualni rang steka ćelija iz rasterskog sloja"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:378
msgid ""
"Calculates the cell-wise percentrank value of a stack of rasters based on an"
" input value raster and writes them to an output raster."
msgstr ""
"Računa procentualni rang vrednosti po ćeliji za stek rastera na osnovu "
"ulaznog rastera vrednosti i upisuje ih u izlazni raster."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:381
msgid ""
"At each cell location, the current value of the value raster is ranked among"
" the respective values in the stack of all overlaid and sorted cell values "
"of the input rasters. For values outside of the the stack value "
"distribution, the algorithm returns NoData because the value cannot be "
"ranked among the cell values."
msgstr ""
"Na svakoj lokaciji ćelije, trenutna vrednost rastera vrednosti se rangira "
"među odgovarajućim vrednostima u steku svih preklopljenih i sortiranih "
"vrednosti ćelija ulaznih rastera. Za vrednosti izvan raspodele vrednosti "
"steka, algoritam vraća NoData jer se vrednost ne može rangirati među "
"vrednostima ćelija."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:406
msgid ""
"Ranking the value raster layer cells. ``NoData`` cells (grey) are ignored."
msgstr ""
"Rangiranje ćelija rasterskog sloja vrednosti. ``NoData`` ćelije (sive) se "
"zanemaruju."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:408
msgid ""
":ref:`qgiscellstackpercentile`, :ref:`qgiscellstackpercentrankfromvalue`"
msgstr ""
":ref:`qgiscellstackpercentile`, :ref:`qgiscellstackpercentrankfromvalue`"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:431
msgid "**Value raster layer**"
msgstr "**Rasterski sloj vrednosti**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:20
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:432
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:789
msgid "``INPUT_VALUE_RASTER``"
msgstr "``INPUT_VALUE_RASTER``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:434
msgid "The layer to rank the values among the stack of all overlaid layers"
msgstr ""
"Sloj čije se vrednosti rangiraju među stekom svih preklopljenih slojeva"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:23
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:435
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:792
msgid "**Value raster band**"
msgstr "**Kanal rastera vrednosti**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:436
msgid "``VALUE_RASTER_BAND``"
msgstr "``VALUE_RASTER_BAND``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:439
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:3231
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:3746
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:4042
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:4048
msgid "Default: 1"
msgstr "Podrazumevano: 1"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:440
msgid "Band of the \"value raster layer\" to compare to"
msgstr "Kanal „rasterskog sloja vrednosti“ sa kojim se poredi"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:549
msgid "**Algorithm ID**: ``native:cellstackpercentrankfromrasterlayer``"
msgstr "**ID algoritma**: ``native:cellstackpercentrankfromrasterlayer``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:559
msgid "Cell statistics"
msgstr "Statistika ćelija"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:561
msgid ""
"Computes per-cell statistics based on input raster layers and for each cell "
"writes the resulting statistics to an output raster. At each cell location, "
"the output value is defined as a function of all overlaid cell values of the"
" input rasters."
msgstr ""
"Računa statistiku po ćeliji na osnovu ulaznih rasterskih slojeva i za svaku "
"ćeliju upisuje rezultujuću statistiku u izlazni raster. Na svakoj lokaciji "
"ćelije, izlazna vrednost se definiše kao funkcija svih preklopljenih "
"vrednosti ćelija ulaznih rastera."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:566
msgid ""
"By default, a NoData cell in ANY of the input layers will result in a NoData"
" cell in the output raster. If the :guilabel:`Ignore NoData values` option "
"is checked, then NoData inputs will be ignored in the statistic calculation."
" This may result in NoData output for locations where all cells are NoData."
msgstr ""
"Podrazumevano, NoData ćelija u BILO KOM od ulaznih slojeva daće NoData "
"ćeliju u izlaznom rasteru. Ako je označena opcija :guilabel:`Zanemari NoData"
" vrednosti`, tada će se NoData ulazi zanemariti u računanju statistike. To "
"može dati NoData izlaz za lokacije gde su sve ćelije NoData."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:572
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Reference layer` parameter specifies an existing raster layer"
" to use as a reference when creating the output raster. The output raster "
"will have the same extent, CRS, and pixel dimensions as this layer."
msgstr ""
"Parametar :guilabel:`Referentni sloj` zadaje postojeći rasterski sloj koji "
"se koristi kao referenca pri pravljenju izlaznog rastera. Izlazni raster "
"imaće isti obuhvat, CRS i dimenzije piksela kao ovaj sloj."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:577
msgid ""
"**Calculation details:** Input raster layers that do not match the cell size"
" of the reference raster layer will be resampled using ``nearest neighbor "
"resampling``. The output raster data type will be set to the most complex "
"data type present in the input datasets except when using the functions "
"``Mean``, ``Standard deviation`` and ``Variance`` (data type is always "
"``Float32`` or ``Float64`` depending on input float type) or ``Count`` and "
"``Variety`` (data type is always ``Int32``)."
msgstr ""
"**Detalji izračunavanja:** Ulazni rasterski slojevi koji ne odgovaraju "
"veličini ćelije referentnog rasterskog sloja biće preuzorkovani pomoću "
"``preuzorkovanja najbližeg suseda``. Tip podataka izlaznog rastera biće "
"postavljen na najsloženiji tip podataka prisutan u ulaznim skupovima "
"podataka, osim pri korišćenju funkcija ``Mean``, ``Standard deviation`` i "
"``Variance`` (tip podataka je uvek ``Float32`` ili ``Float64`` u zavisnosti "
"od ulaznog float tipa) ili ``Count`` i ``Variety`` (tip podataka je uvek "
"``Int32``)."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:586
msgid ""
"``Count``: The count statistic will always result in the number of cells "
"without NoData values at the current cell location."
msgstr ""
"``Count``: statistika broja uvek daje broj ćelija bez NoData vrednosti na "
"trenutnoj lokaciji ćelije."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:589
msgid ""
"``Median``: If the number of input layers is even, the median will be "
"calculated as the arithmetic mean of the two middle values of the ordered "
"cell input values."
msgstr ""
"``Median``: ako je broj ulaznih slojeva paran, medijana se računa kao "
"aritmetička sredina dve srednje vrednosti uređenih ulaznih vrednosti ćelija."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:592
msgid ""
"``Minority/Majority``: If no unique minority or majority could be found, the"
" result is NoData, except all input cell values are equal."
msgstr ""
"``Minority/Majority``: ako se ne može pronaći jedinstvena manjina ili "
"većina, rezultat je NoData, osim ako su sve ulazne vrednosti ćelija jednake."

