#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:1839
msgid "Greater than frequency"
msgstr "Učestalost veće od"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:1841
msgid ""
"Evaluates on a cell-by-cell basis the frequency (number of times) the values"
" of an input stack of rasters are equal to the value of a value raster. The "
"output raster extent and resolution is defined by the input raster layer and"
" is always of ``Int32`` type."
msgstr ""
"Izračunava po ćeliji učestalost (broj puta) kada su vrednosti ulaznog steka "
"rastera jednake vrednosti rastera vrednosti. Obuhvat i rezolucija izlaznog "
"rastera definisani su ulaznim rasterskim slojem i uvek su tipa ``Int32``."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:1854
msgid ""
"For each cell in the output raster, the value represents the number of times"
" that the corresponding cells in the list of rasters are greater than the "
"value raster. ``NoData`` cells (grey) are taken into account."
msgstr ""
"Za svaku ćeliju u izlaznom rasteru, vrednost predstavlja broj puta kada su "
"odgovarajuće ćelije u listi rastera veće od rastera vrednosti. ``NoData`` "
"ćelije (sive) se uzimaju u obzir."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:1858
msgid ":ref:`qgisequaltofrequency`, :ref:`qgislessthanfrequency`"
msgstr ":ref:`qgisequaltofrequency`, :ref:`qgislessthanfrequency`"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:1869
msgid "**Algorithm ID**: ``native:greaterthanfrequency``"
msgstr "**ID algoritma**: ``native:greaterthanfrequency``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:1879
msgid "Highest position in raster stack"
msgstr "Najviši položaj u steku rastera"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:1881
msgid ""
"Evaluates on a cell-by-cell basis the position of the raster with the "
"highest value in a stack of rasters. Position counts start with 1 and range "
"to the total number of input rasters. The order of the input rasters is "
"relevant for the algorithm. If multiple rasters feature the highest value, "
"the first raster will be used for the position value."
msgstr ""
"Izračunava po ćeliji položaj rastera sa najvišom vrednošću u steku rastera. "
"Brojanje položaja počinje od 1 i ide do ukupnog broja ulaznih rastera. "
"Redosled ulaznih rastera je bitan za algoritam. Ako više rastera ima najvišu"
" vrednost, za vrednost položaja koristiće se prvi raster."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:1887
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:2081
msgid ""
"If multiband rasters are used in the data raster stack, the algorithm will "
"always perform the analysis on the first band of the rasters - use GDAL to "
"use other bands in the analysis. Any NoData cells in the raster layer stack "
"will result in a NoData cell in the output raster unless the \"ignore "
"NoData\" parameter is checked. The output NoData value can be set manually. "
"The output rasters extent and resolution is defined by a reference raster "
"layer and is always of ``Int32`` type."
msgstr ""
"Ako se u steku rastera podataka koriste višekanalni rasteri, algoritam će "
"analizu uvek vršiti na prvom kanalu rastera - koristite GDAL za korišćenje "
"drugih kanala u analizi. Sve NoData ćelije u steku rasterskih slojeva daće "
"NoData ćeliju u izlaznom rasteru, osim ako je označen parametar „zanemari "
"NoData“. Izlazna NoData vrednost može se postaviti ručno. Obuhvat i "
"rezolucija izlaznih rastera definisani su referentnim rasterskim slojem i "
"uvek su tipa ``Int32``."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:1898
msgid ":ref:`qgislowestpositioninrasterstack`"
msgstr ":ref:`qgislowestpositioninrasterstack`"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:21
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:1920
msgid "List of raster layers to compare with"
msgstr "Lista rasterskih slojeva sa kojima se poredi"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:32
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:1931
msgid ""
"If unchecked, any NoData cells in the data layer stack will result in a "
"NoData cell in the output raster"
msgstr ""
"Ako nije označeno, sve NoData ćelije u steku slojeva podataka daće NoData "
"ćeliju u izlaznom rasteru"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:39
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:1938
