#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:2350
msgid ""
"Specification of the output raster containing the result. :ref:`One of "
"<output_parameter_widget>`:"
msgstr ""
"Specifikacija izlaznog rastera koji sadrži rezultat. :ref:`Jedno od "
"<output_parameter_widget>`:"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:2023
msgid "**Algorithm ID**: ``native:highestpositioninrasterstack``"
msgstr "**ID algoritma**: ``native:highestpositioninrasterstack``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:2033
msgid "Less than frequency"
msgstr "Učestalost manja od"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:2035
msgid ""
"Evaluates on a cell-by-cell basis the frequency (number of times) the values"
" of an input stack of rasters are less than the value of a value raster. The"
" output raster extent and resolution is defined by the input raster layer "
"and is always of ``Int32`` type."
msgstr ""
"Izračunava po ćeliji učestalost (broj puta) kada su vrednosti ulaznog steka "
"rastera manje od vrednosti rastera vrednosti. Obuhvat i rezolucija izlaznog "
"rastera definisani su ulaznim rasterskim slojem i uvek su tipa ``Int32``."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:2048
msgid ""
"For each cell in the output raster, the value represents the number of times"
" that the corresponding cells in the list of rasters are less than the value"
" raster. ``NoData`` cells (grey) are taken into account."
msgstr ""
"Za svaku ćeliju u izlaznom rasteru, vrednost predstavlja broj puta kada su "
"odgovarajuće ćelije u listi rastera manje od rastera vrednosti. ``NoData`` "
"ćelije (sive) se uzimaju u obzir."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:2052
msgid ":ref:`qgisequaltofrequency`, :ref:`qgisgreaterthanfrequency`"
msgstr ":ref:`qgisequaltofrequency`, :ref:`qgisgreaterthanfrequency`"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:2063
msgid "**Algorithm ID**: ``native:lessthanfrequency``"
msgstr "**ID algoritma**: ``native:lessthanfrequency``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:2073
msgid "Lowest position in raster stack"
msgstr "Najniži položaj u steku rastera"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:2075
msgid ""
"Evaluates on a cell-by-cell basis the position of the raster with the lowest"
" value in a stack of rasters. Position counts start with 1 and range to the "
"total number of input rasters. The order of the input rasters is relevant "
"for the algorithm. If multiple rasters feature the lowest value, the first "
"raster will be used for the position value."
msgstr ""
"Izračunava po ćeliji položaj rastera sa najnižom vrednošću u steku rastera. "
"Brojanje položaja počinje od 1 i ide do ukupnog broja ulaznih rastera. "
"Redosled ulaznih rastera je bitan za algoritam. Ako više rastera ima najnižu"
" vrednost, za vrednost položaja koristiće se prvi raster."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:2092
msgid ":ref:`qgishighestpositioninrasterstack`"
msgstr ":ref:`qgishighestpositioninrasterstack`"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:2103
msgid "**Algorithm ID**: ``native:lowestpositioninrasterstack``"
msgstr "**ID algoritma**: ``native:lowestpositioninrasterstack``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:2113
msgid "Raster boolean AND"
msgstr "Rasterski logički AND"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:2114
msgid ""
"Calculates the boolean ``AND`` for a set of input rasters. If all of the "
"input rasters have a non-zero value for a pixel, that pixel will be set to "
"``1`` in the output raster. If any of the input rasters have ``0`` values "
"for the pixel it will be set to ``0`` in the output raster."
msgstr ""
"Računa logičko ``AND`` za skup ulaznih rastera. Ako svi ulazni rasteri imaju"
" vrednost različitu od nule za neki piksel, taj piksel biće postavljen na "
"``1`` u izlaznom rasteru. Ako bilo koji od ulaznih rastera ima vrednost "
"``0`` za piksel, biće postavljen na ``0`` u izlaznom rasteru."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:2120
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:2297
msgid ""
"The reference layer parameter specifies an existing raster layer to use as a"
" reference when creating the output raster. The output raster will have the "
"same extent, CRS, and pixel dimensions as this layer."
msgstr ""
"Parametar referentnog sloja zadaje postojeći rasterski sloj koji se koristi "
"kao referenca pri pravljenju izlaznog rastera. Izlazni raster imaće isti "
"obuhvat, CRS i dimenzije piksela kao ovaj sloj."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:2125
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:2302
msgid ""
"By default, a NoData pixel in ANY of the input layers will result in a "
"NoData pixel in the output raster. If the :guilabel:`Treat NoData values as "
"false` option is checked, then NoData inputs will be treated the same as a "
"``0`` input value."
msgstr ""
"Podrazumevano, NoData piksel u BILO KOM od ulaznih slojeva daće NoData "
"piksel u izlaznom rasteru. Ako je označena opcija :guilabel:`Tretiraj NoData"
" vrednosti kao netačne`, tada će se NoData ulazi tretirati isto kao ulazna "
"vrednost ``0``."

