#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:3135
msgid ""
"Raster layer used to calculate the centroids that will be used as reference "
"when determining the zones in the output layer. One of:"
msgstr ""
"Rasterski sloj koji se koristi za računanje centroida koji će se koristiti "
"kao referenca pri određivanju zona u izlaznom sloju. Jedno od:"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:3139
msgid ""
"0 --- Input layer: zones are determined by sampling the zone raster layer "
"value at the centroid of each pixel from the source raster layer"
msgstr ""
"0 --- Ulazni sloj: zone se određuju uzorkovanjem vrednosti rasterskog sloja "
"zona u centroidu svakog piksela izvornog rasterskog sloja"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:3141
msgid ""
"1 --- Zones layer: the input raster layer will be sampled at the centroid of"
" each pixel from the zones raster layer"
msgstr ""
"1 --- Sloj zona: ulazni rasterski sloj biće uzorkovan u centroidu svakog "
"piksela rasterskog sloja zona"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:3175
