msgstr "**ID algoritma**: ``native:rasterlayerzonalstats``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:3206
msgid "Raster minimum/maximum"
msgstr "Minimum/maksimum rastera"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:3207
msgid ""
"Extracts the minimum and maximum pixel values from a specified band of a "
"raster layer. If multiple pixels share the same minimum or maximum value, "
"only one of them will be included in the output."
msgstr ""
"Izdvaja minimalnu i maksimalnu vrednost piksela iz zadatog kanala rasterskog"
" sloja. Ako više piksela deli istu minimalnu ili maksimalnu vrednost, samo "
"jedan od njih biće uključen u izlaz."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:3226
msgid ""
"Raster layer from which to extract the minimum and maximum pixel values."
msgstr ""
"Rasterski sloj iz kojeg se izdvajaju minimalna i maksimalna vrednost "
"piksela."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:3232
msgid ""
"The band of the raster to analyze. If the raster is multiband, specify the "
"band number (starting from 1)."
msgstr ""
"Kanal rastera koji se analizira. Ako je raster višekanalni, zadajte broj "
"kanala (počev od 1)."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:3233
msgid "**Extract**"
msgstr "**Izdvoj**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:3234
msgid "``EXTREMA``"
msgstr "``EXTREMA``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:3237
