"Specification of the output layer. :ref:`One of <output_parameter_widget>`:"
msgstr ""
"Specifikacija izlaznog sloja. :ref:`Jedno od <output_parameter_widget>`:"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:3269
msgid ""
"Vector layer with point features at the locations of the minimum and/or "
"maximum pixel values."
msgstr ""
"Vektorski sloj sa tačkastim objektima na lokacijama minimalnih i/ili "
"maksimalnih vrednosti piksela."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:3274
msgid "**Algorithm ID**: ``native:rasterminmax``"
msgstr "**ID algoritma**: ``native:rasterminmax``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:3284
msgid "Raster rank"
msgstr "Rang rastera"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:3285
msgid "``Added in 3.44``"
msgstr "``Dodato u 3.44``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:3287
msgid ""
"Performs a cell-by-cell analysis in which output values match the rank of a "
"sorted list of overlapping cell values from input layers. The output raster "
"will be multi-band if multiple ranks are provided. If multiband rasters are "
"used in the data raster stack, the algorithm will always perform the "
"analysis on the first band of the rasters."
msgstr ""
"Vrši analizu po ćeliji u kojoj izlazne vrednosti odgovaraju rangu sortirane "
"liste preklapajućih vrednosti ćelija iz ulaznih slojeva. Izlazni raster biće"
" višekanalni ako je zadato više rangova. Ako se u steku rastera podataka "
"koriste višekanalni rasteri, algoritam će analizu uvek vršiti na prvom "
"kanalu rastera."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:3296
msgid ""
"Raster rank result for rank 1 (minimum value). NoData cells in any input "
"raster result in a NoData output cell."
msgstr ""
"Rezultat ranga rastera za rang 1 (minimalna vrednost). NoData ćelije u bilo "
"kom ulaznom rasteru daju NoData izlaznu ćeliju."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:3298
msgid ""
":ref:`qgiscellstackpercentrankfromvalue`, :ref:`qgiscellstackpercentile`, "
":ref:`qgiscellstackpercentrankfromrasterlayer`, :ref:`qgiscellstatistics`, "
":ref:`qgisrastercalc`"
msgstr ""
":ref:`qgiscellstackpercentrankfromvalue`, :ref:`qgiscellstackpercentile`, "
":ref:`qgiscellstackpercentrankfromrasterlayer`, :ref:`qgiscellstatistics`, "
":ref:`qgisrastercalc`"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:3318
msgid "Input raster layer(s) to calculate the rank from."
msgstr "Ulazni rasterski sloj(evi) za koje se računa rang."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:3319
msgid "**Rank**"
msgstr "**Rang**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:3320
msgid "``RANKS``"
msgstr "``RANKS``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:3321
msgid "[numeric: integer] [list]"
msgstr "[numerički: ceo broj] [lista]"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:3323
msgid "Default: [1]"
msgstr "Podrazumevano: [1]"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:3324
msgid ""
"List of ranks to calculate for each pixel in the sorted list of cells values"
" from the input rasters. Cells whose values match the given rank(s) are kept"
" in the output layer. The ranks are 1-based, meaning that the first rank is "
"1. Negative values are also supported."
msgstr ""
"Lista rangova koji se računaju za svaki piksel u sortiranoj listi vrednosti "
"ćelija iz ulaznih rastera. Ćelije čije vrednosti odgovaraju zadatom "
"rangu(ovima) zadržavaju se u izlaznom sloju. Rangovi počinju od 1, što znači"
" da je prvi rang 1. Podržane su i negativne vrednosti."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:3329
msgid "**NoData value handling**"
msgstr "**Rukovanje NoData vrednostima**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:3330
msgid "``NODATA_HANDLING``"
msgstr "``NODATA_HANDLING``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:3334
msgid "Choose how to handle NoData values in the input raster:"
msgstr "Izaberite kako da se rukuje NoData vrednostima u ulaznom rasteru:"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:3336
msgid ""
"0 --- Exclude NoData from values lists: will not include NoData values in "
"the list of pixel values when calculating ranks."
msgstr ""
"0 --- Isključi NoData iz listi vrednosti: NoData vrednosti neće biti "
"uključene u listu vrednosti piksela pri računanju rangova."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:3337
msgid ""
"1 --- Presence of NoData in a values list results in NoData output cells: "
"the output raster will have NoData values in the corresponding locations."
msgstr ""
"1 --- Prisustvo NoData u listi vrednosti daje NoData izlazne ćelije: izlazni"
" raster imaće NoData vrednosti na odgovarajućim lokacijama."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:3338
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:3405
msgid "**Ranked**"
msgstr "**Rangirano**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:3343
msgid ""
"Specification of the output raster containing the rank values. :ref:`One of "
"<output_parameter_widget>`:"
msgstr ""
"Specifikacija izlaznog rastera koji sadrži vrednosti ranga. :ref:`Jedno od "
"<output_parameter_widget>`:"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:3375
msgid "**Output cell size**"
msgstr "**Veličina izlazne ćelije**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:3378
msgid "``CELL_SIZE``"
msgstr "``CELL_SIZE``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:3408
msgid "Output raster layer containing the result."
msgstr "Izlazni rasterski sloj koji sadrži rezultat."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:3413
msgid "**Algorithm ID**: ``native:rasterrank``"
msgstr "**ID algoritma**: ``native:rasterrank``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:3423
msgid "Raster surface volume"
msgstr "Zapremina površine rastera"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:3424
msgid ""
"Calculates the volume under a raster surface relative to a given base level."
" This is mainly useful for Digital Elevation Models (DEM)."
msgstr ""
"Računa zapreminu ispod rasterske površine u odnosu na zadati bazni nivo. Ovo"
" je uglavnom korisno za digitalne modele visina (DEM)."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:3439
msgid "**INPUT layer**"
msgstr "**ULAZNI sloj**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:3442
msgid "Input raster, representing a surface"
msgstr "Ulazni raster koji predstavlja površinu"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:3448
msgid ""
"If the raster is multiband, choose the band that shall define the surface."
msgstr "Ako je raster višekanalni, izaberite kanal koji definiše površinu."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:3450
msgid "**Base level**"
msgstr "**Bazni nivo**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:3451
msgid "``LEVEL``"
msgstr "``LEVEL``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:3455
msgid ""
"Define a base or reference value. This base is used in the volume "
"calculation according to the ``Method`` parameter (see below)."
msgstr ""
"Definišite baznu ili referentnu vrednost. Ova baza se koristi u računanju "
"zapremine prema parametru ``Metod`` (pogledajte ispod)."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:3463
msgid ""
"Define the method for the volume calculation given by the difference between"
" the raster pixel value and the ``Base level``. Options:"
msgstr ""
"Definišite metod za računanje zapremine dat razlikom između vrednosti "
"piksela rastera i ``Baznog nivoa``. Opcije:"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:3468
msgid ""
"0 --- Count Only Above Base Level: only pixels above the base level will add"
" to the volume."
msgstr ""
"0 --- Broj samo iznad baznog nivoa: zapremini se dodaju samo pikseli iznad "
"baznog nivoa."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:3470
msgid ""
"1 --- Count Only Below Base Level: only pixels below the base level will add"
" to the volume."
msgstr ""
"1 --- Broj samo ispod baznog nivoa: zapremini se dodaju samo pikseli ispod "
"baznog nivoa."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:3472
msgid ""
"2 --- Subtract Volumes Below Base level: pixels above the base level will "
"add to the volume, pixels below the base level will subtract from the "
"volume."
msgstr ""
"2 --- Oduzmi zapremine ispod baznog nivoa: pikseli iznad baznog nivoa se "
"dodaju zapremini, pikseli ispod baznog nivoa se oduzimaju od zapremine."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:3475
msgid ""
"3 --- Add Volumes Below Base level: Add the volume regardless whether the "
"pixel is above or below the base level. This is equivalent to sum the "
"absolute values of the difference between the pixel value and the base "
"level."
msgstr ""
"3 --- Dodaj zapremine ispod baznog nivoa: dodaje zapreminu bez obzira na to "
"da li je piksel iznad ili ispod baznog nivoa. Ovo je ekvivalentno sabiranju "
"apsolutnih vrednosti razlike između vrednosti piksela i baznog nivoa."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasteranalysis.rst:3479
